574
00:31:53,820 --> 00:31:55,620
the taste is different from last time.

575
00:31:57,140 --> 00:31:58,536
Why don't I get you another plate?

576
00:32:00,340 --> 00:32:00,970
No thanks.

577
00:32:00,970 --> 00:32:01,490
Just leave it.

578
00:32:02,250 --> 00:32:02,860
Please enjoy.

579
00:32:07,710 --> 00:32:08,810
It's the usual taste.

580
00:32:08,900 --> 00:32:10,970
I thought Father ruined it today.

581
00:32:11,380 --> 00:32:12,860
Try it again, Sir.

582
00:32:27,336 --> 00:32:29,672
Do you still think
something's wrong with the taste?

583
00:32:30,344 --> 00:32:32,664
Could it be that the girl
from last time isn't here

584
00:32:32,680 --> 00:32:34,490
so you lost your appetite?

585
00:32:34,900 --> 00:32:35,320
Yes.

586
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:37,790
Good food tastes better when shared.

587
00:32:37,860 --> 00:32:38,310
Han.

588
00:32:38,510 --> 00:32:39,310
Get back to work.

589
00:32:40,136 --> 00:32:42,008
Go to the backyard and wash the dishes.

590
00:32:44,570 --> 00:32:44,970
My Lord.

591
00:32:52,580 --> 00:32:53,470
I found out

592
00:32:53,580 --> 00:32:55,064
the identity of the old house owner.

593
00:32:55,080 --> 00:32:56,210
His name was Zheng Sheng.

594
00:32:56,660 --> 00:32:58,310
He was a foundryman at Foundry Bureau.

595
00:32:59,660 --> 00:33:00,810
Nanling Foundry Bureau?

596
00:33:01,840 --> 00:33:02,360
Yes.

597
00:33:03,290 --> 00:33:04,570
Nanling Foundry Bureau

598
00:33:04,860 --> 00:33:07,250
had an accident two months ago.

599
00:33:08,900 --> 00:33:10,664
Several foundrymen were burned to death.

600
00:33:10,900 --> 00:33:12,050
Zheng Sheng is also among them.

601
00:33:13,250 --> 00:33:14,080
How did you know?

602
00:33:15,688 --> 00:33:17,768
When I first
looked into the military equipment case,

603
00:33:17,784 --> 00:33:18,950
He Zhenwen had mentioned it.

604
00:33:20,360 --> 00:33:21,270
But

605
00:33:21,270 --> 00:33:22,392
he only mentioned it briefly.

606
00:33:22,660 --> 00:33:23,860
I didn't delve into it.

607
00:33:24,510 --> 00:33:25,880
Now that I think about it,

608
00:33:26,730 --> 00:33:27,880
perhaps the fire

609
00:33:28,070 --> 00:33:29,530
wasn't an accident.

610
00:33:33,070 --> 00:33:35,710
You said before that the military
equipment case isn't over.

611
00:33:36,290 --> 00:33:36,950
Could this

612
00:33:37,380 --> 00:33:38,990
be the key?

613
00:33:41,672 --> 00:33:43,570
Did you find any clues
about the footprints?

614
00:33:45,530 --> 00:33:46,160
Not yet.

615
00:33:49,810 --> 00:33:51,080
Although Zheng Sheng is dead,

616
00:33:51,384 --> 00:33:53,592
he should have been
in a relationship with a woman.

617
00:33:54,070 --> 00:33:54,950
This woman

618
00:33:55,380 --> 00:33:56,550
doesn't know martial arts.

619
00:33:57,340 --> 00:33:58,120
Only by finding her

620
00:33:59,030 --> 00:34:00,140
can we know

621
00:34:00,360 --> 00:34:01,570
the relationship

622
00:34:01,570 --> 00:34:03,030
between them and the Yan Sisters.

623
00:34:15,490 --> 00:34:16,100
Give me.

624
00:34:23,450 --> 00:34:24,240
Give it back to me!

625
00:34:27,970 --> 00:34:29,910
Mother, what are they eating?

626
00:34:30,240 --> 00:34:31,700
If you don't study hard,

627
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:33,030
you'll end up

628
00:34:33,032 --> 00:34:34,720
begging and eating
kitchen slop like them.

629
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:37,280
(It is said that Zhao Wu
married and had children)

630
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:38,696
outside before entering the palace.

631
00:34:39,200 --> 00:34:40,070
His descendants

632
00:34:40,120 --> 00:34:41,720
(have lived in Nanling for a long time.)

633
00:34:41,760 --> 00:34:43,200
(These are the oranges I planted.)

634
00:34:43,200 --> 00:34:43,800
(Try them.)

635
00:34:43,870 --> 00:34:45,140
I'm just used to separating

636
00:34:45,220 --> 00:34:46,700
rice and dishes.

637
00:34:47,300 --> 00:34:48,050
Ayan.

638
00:34:48,050 --> 00:34:49,030
Go home first.

639
00:34:56,890 --> 00:34:58,780
(Could the mysterious footprints
be Ayan's?)

640
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:01,070
(Does she know Zheng Sheng?)

641
00:35:02,970 --> 00:35:04,910
(What does the Yans
have to do with them?)

642
00:35:15,140 --> 00:35:16,660
My husband's name is Zheng Sheng.

643
00:35:17,910 --> 00:35:20,080
He's a foundryman
at Nanling Foundry Bureau.

644
00:35:22,552 --> 00:35:24,050
He died in the fire at Foundry Bureau

645
00:35:26,970 --> 00:35:28,390
two months ago.

646
00:35:46,810 --> 00:35:49,330
(Zheng Sheng, Blacksmith
Nanling Foundry Bureau)

647
00:36:26,080 --> 00:36:27,580
(You mean)

648
00:36:27,720 --> 00:36:28,870
(Zheng Sheng found)

649
00:36:29,240 --> 00:36:31,280
(that all the workshops except Grade A)

650
00:36:31,490 --> 00:36:33,050
were using scrap metal?

651
00:36:35,050 --> 00:36:36,240
Sheng can guarantee

652
00:36:37,120 --> 00:36:39,530
that all Grade A forged swords

653
00:36:39,660 --> 00:36:40,760
can cut through iron

654
00:36:40,830 --> 00:36:41,830
and aren't bad products.

655
00:36:42,660 --> 00:36:44,830
But their whereabouts
are unknown after being produced

656
00:36:45,030 --> 00:36:46,140
by Grade A and sent away.

657
00:36:47,200 --> 00:36:50,140
Sheng was burned alive in the workshop

658
00:36:51,100 --> 00:36:53,070
not long after he mentioned this to me.

659
00:36:55,490 --> 00:36:56,910
The officials said

660
00:36:57,160 --> 00:36:59,336
it was due to improper operation
by the foundrymen.

661
00:37:00,140 --> 00:37:01,890
But Sheng and those old blacksmiths

662
00:37:02,120 --> 00:37:03,330
are diligent and dedicated.

663
00:37:03,330 --> 00:37:04,830
They would never neglect their duties.

664
00:37:05,390 --> 00:37:07,490
Sheng must have been killed

665
00:37:08,070 --> 00:37:10,050
after discovering their secret.

666
00:37:12,240 --> 00:37:13,100
Later,

667
00:37:15,160 --> 00:37:17,760
I tried finding
the families of the other foundrymen,

668
00:37:20,300 --> 00:37:21,800
but they all left Nanling

669
00:37:23,070 --> 00:37:24,510
overnight.

670
00:37:25,950 --> 00:37:27,660
Sheng and I have always been low-key.

671
00:37:29,050 --> 00:37:30,260
I guess

672
00:37:31,510 --> 00:37:32,910
that's why I escaped.

673
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:36,750
The businessmen and officials in Nanling
collude with each other.

674
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:37,848
There's no one you can trust.

675
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:41,330
They downplayed the fire.

676
00:37:43,330 --> 00:37:45,030
I've carefully stayed hidden

677
00:37:46,870 --> 00:37:48,490
so that I can seek justice for Sheng

678
00:37:50,450 --> 00:37:51,970
someday.

679
00:37:55,220 --> 00:37:56,070
Miss Jiang.

680
00:37:58,570 --> 00:38:00,280
I beg you to take me to see Lord.

681
00:38:00,570 --> 00:38:02,390
Lord can sacrifice
his relatives for justice.

682
00:38:02,570 --> 00:38:04,660
He must have a way
to get justice for Zheng Sheng.

683
00:38:04,800 --> 00:38:05,950
Get up first.

684
00:38:08,050 --> 00:38:09,070
Do you have proof?

685
00:38:10,530 --> 00:38:11,160
Yes,

686
00:38:12,300 --> 00:38:13,010
but

687
00:38:14,240 --> 00:38:15,970
I can only hand it over to Lord myself.

688
00:38:17,830 --> 00:38:18,700
Miss Jiang.

689
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:20,410
I beg you.

690
00:38:34,720 --> 00:38:35,580
Miss Ayan.

691
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:38,300
Is this the proof?

692
00:38:40,168 --> 00:38:41,470
Sheng can't afford jewelry.

693
00:38:41,470 --> 00:38:42,280
I made this for you.

694
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:44,280
(He made a knife ring for me.)

695
00:38:48,350 --> 00:38:49,550
You can look into it.

696
00:38:49,560 --> 00:38:50,890
The casting material of it

697
00:38:50,910 --> 00:38:53,050
is different
from those produced by other workshops.

698
00:38:53,288 --> 00:38:54,008
Your Lordship.

699
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:55,530
Ayan won't lie.

700
00:38:55,620 --> 00:38:56,700
Help her.

701
00:39:01,850 --> 00:39:02,570
Miss Ayan.

702
00:39:04,620 --> 00:39:06,050
This is a big deal.

703
00:39:06,530 --> 00:39:08,100
Stay at Changfeng Estate first.

704
00:39:08,216 --> 00:39:09,864
Once I've investigated this thoroughly,

705
00:39:09,990 --> 00:39:11,160
I'll give you an explanation.

706
00:39:14,890 --> 00:39:15,970
To be safe,

707
00:39:16,350 --> 00:39:17,470
don't mention this

708
00:39:17,990 --> 00:39:18,760
to anyone else.

709
00:39:21,064 --> 00:39:22,248
Thank you, Your Lordship.

710
00:39:22,490 --> 00:39:23,430
Thank you, Your Lordship.

711
00:39:24,570 --> 00:39:26,660
I compared the footprints
with Miss Ayan's shoes

712
00:39:26,800 --> 00:39:27,970
and they're a match.

713
00:39:28,530 --> 00:39:29,410
How is Miss Ayan

714
00:39:29,660 --> 00:39:31,430
related to the Yans?

715
00:39:32,470 --> 00:39:33,490
You mentioned

716
00:39:33,740 --> 00:39:34,930
that Zhao Wu's wife

717
00:39:34,990 --> 00:39:36,160
was once a slave.

718
00:39:37,180 --> 00:39:37,740
Yes.

719
00:39:38,100 --> 00:39:39,800
She seems to be freed from slavery

720
00:39:39,850 --> 00:39:41,432
only after Zhao Wu entered the palace.

721
00:39:42,260 --> 00:39:43,720
Slaves often ate kitchen slop.

722
00:39:43,910 --> 00:39:45,430
Many people who escaped slavery

723
00:39:45,660 --> 00:39:47,280
would be traumatized.

724
00:39:48,410 --> 00:39:49,800
Miss Ayan doesn't like to mix food

725
00:39:49,910 --> 00:39:52,470
when she cooks.

726
00:39:54,100 --> 00:39:54,780
Could

727
00:39:55,740 --> 00:39:57,160
Ayan be a descendant of Zhao Wu?

728
00:40:01,720 --> 00:40:02,200
My Lord.

729
00:40:08,660 --> 00:40:10,050
Why is Miss Ayan here?

730
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:12,990
Don't be afraid.

731
00:40:13,050 --> 00:40:14,050
He's not a bad guy.

732
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:15,700
Go back first.

733
00:40:15,700 --> 00:40:16,700
I'll find you later.

734
00:40:24,010 --> 00:40:26,180
Lord has begun
to doubt our relationship.

735
00:40:26,490 --> 00:40:28,100
We should be more cautious from now on.

736
00:40:30,530 --> 00:40:31,970
What is my relationship

737
00:40:32,100 --> 00:40:33,200
with you?

738
00:40:35,140 --> 00:40:36,910
You have no shame, Commander Wei.

739
00:40:36,952 --> 00:40:38,620
I guess
you're not afraid of being exposed.

740
00:40:38,720 --> 00:40:40,100
I worried for nothing.

741
00:40:44,720 --> 00:40:46,950
Did something happen to Miss Ayan?

742
00:40:49,530 --> 00:40:50,620
No comments.

743
00:40:52,910 --> 00:40:54,800
You just said I'm not a bad guy.

744
00:40:55,576 --> 00:40:56,744
These are two different things.

745
00:41:03,430 --> 00:41:04,950
Why did Ayan meet Pei Yan?

746
00:41:06,140 --> 00:41:06,970
I'm afraid

747
00:41:07,100 --> 00:41:09,180
it's because of the fire
at Foundry Bureau.

748
00:41:10,680 --> 00:41:12,050
She must have been following us

749
00:41:12,220 --> 00:41:13,600
to find an opportunity

750
00:41:13,700 --> 00:41:14,870
to complain to Pei Yan.

751
00:41:16,100 --> 00:41:18,010
If she tells him about Yan Sisters,

752
00:41:18,300 --> 00:41:19,800
won't we be put in a passive position?

753
00:41:21,220 --> 00:41:22,200
That depends

754
00:41:22,430 --> 00:41:24,970
on how much
Miss Ayan knows about Yan Sisters.

755
00:41:26,570 --> 00:41:27,240
However,

756
00:41:27,700 --> 00:41:29,470
Pei Yan

757
00:41:29,950 --> 00:41:32,030
has more pressing matters right now.

758
00:41:35,200 --> 00:41:36,430
Did we get it wrong?

759
00:41:36,488 --> 00:41:38,936
Is there a different story
to the military equipment case?

760
00:41:39,180 --> 00:41:40,070
Could Foundry Bureau

761
00:41:40,070 --> 00:41:41,950
have hidden a batch of premium weapons?

762
00:41:42,490 --> 00:41:43,700
But where did they go?

763
00:41:44,870 --> 00:41:47,240
We can only close the military
equipment case with corruption.

764
00:41:47,950 --> 00:41:49,864
Otherwise,
if His Majesty's suspicion resurfaces,

765
00:41:49,944 --> 00:41:51,240
our return to the imperial court

766
00:41:51,490 --> 00:41:52,700
will be delayed.

767
00:41:54,720 --> 00:41:55,620
One more thing.

768
00:41:56,390 --> 00:41:57,390
I found out

769
00:41:57,416 --> 00:41:59,070
that Zheng Sheng
who Miss Ayan mentioned

770
00:41:59,070 --> 00:42:00,200
was the owner of the old house

771
00:42:00,200 --> 00:42:01,910
that I found when I was
looking for the traces

772
00:42:01,910 --> 00:42:03,140
of the Yan Sisters some time ago.

773
00:42:06,870 --> 00:42:09,450
I can't believe
they're linked to the Yan Sisters.

774
00:42:10,920 --> 00:42:13,180
I'll see if I can find out
more information from Miss Ayan.

775
00:42:13,570 --> 00:42:13,970
No.

776
00:42:14,470 --> 00:42:15,430
Our priority now

777
00:42:15,784 --> 00:42:16,970
is the military equipment case.

778
00:42:18,140 --> 00:42:19,350
Go to Foundry Bureau

779
00:42:19,350 --> 00:42:21,768
to find a list of the foundrymen
that included Zheng Sheng.

780
00:42:21,950 --> 00:42:23,200
Don't alert anyone.

781
00:42:24,720 --> 00:42:26,490
As for the Yan Sisters,

782
00:42:27,370 --> 00:42:28,800
it won't be hard

783
00:42:29,180 --> 00:42:31,450
to get information out of Ayan

784
00:42:31,510 --> 00:42:32,570
since she trusts me.

785
00:42:32,990 --> 00:42:33,760
Shaojun.

786
00:42:34,140 --> 00:42:35,200
Are you free?

787
00:42:36,200 --> 00:42:37,100
Commander Wei?

788
00:42:38,072 --> 00:42:39,070
Sanlang mustn't find out

789
00:42:39,224 --> 00:42:40,570
about the military equipment case

790
00:42:41,010 --> 00:42:42,350
before we find the truth.

791
00:42:42,970 --> 00:42:43,870
Leave first.

792
00:42:44,390 --> 00:42:45,100
Yes.

793
00:42:49,470 --> 00:42:50,470
Sanlang, come in.

794
00:42:55,208 --> 00:42:56,632
You wanted to see me, Sanlang?

795
00:42:57,350 --> 00:42:58,600
Now that the case is closed,

796
00:42:58,740 --> 00:43:00,050
I'd like to ask

797
00:43:00,350 --> 00:43:01,800
when you plan to return to Qingkang.

798
00:43:02,470 --> 00:43:05,220
The military equipment case
still needs to be wrapped up.

799
00:43:05,220 --> 00:43:06,180
Returning hastily

800
00:43:06,180 --> 00:43:07,600
might do His Majesty wrong.

801
00:43:07,950 --> 00:43:08,680
Why don't you

802
00:43:09,930 --> 00:43:11,010
go back first, Sanlang?

803
00:43:12,530 --> 00:43:13,990
If I go back

804
00:43:14,200 --> 00:43:15,350
without you,

805
00:43:15,350 --> 00:43:17,070
won't that make me negligent?

806
00:43:19,140 --> 00:43:20,470
I didn't think it through.

807
00:43:20,470 --> 00:43:21,300
You'll

808
00:43:21,700 --> 00:43:23,140
have to stay at Changfeng Estate

809
00:43:23,490 --> 00:43:25,200
a little longer.

810
00:43:27,550 --> 00:43:28,530
You're too kind, Shaojun.

811
00:43:32,910 --> 00:43:33,660
Speaking of which,

812
00:43:33,660 --> 00:43:35,660
I saw Miss Ayan outside just now.

813
00:43:36,010 --> 00:43:37,140
Ci was scared of boredom,

814
00:43:37,288 --> 00:43:39,910
so I allowed her to bring Miss Ayan back
for a small get-together.

815
00:43:42,200 --> 00:43:43,240
I see.

816
00:43:51,660 --> 00:43:53,100
Spy on Pei Yan and Ayan.

817
00:43:53,620 --> 00:43:54,890
Let me know

818
00:43:55,080 --> 00:43:56,360
if they meet in private.

819
00:43:56,720 --> 00:43:57,030
Yes.

820
00:44:06,640 --> 00:44:07,950
Just stay here.

821
00:44:07,990 --> 00:44:09,368
Let me know if you need anything.

822
00:44:09,780 --> 00:44:10,660
Miss Jiang.

823
00:44:10,950 --> 00:44:12,700
I don't know how I can thank you.

824
00:44:13,760 --> 00:44:14,800
You don't have to thank me.

825
00:44:14,970 --> 00:44:16,470
You should thank Lord.

826
00:44:17,430 --> 00:44:18,200
Yes,

827
00:44:19,970 --> 00:44:20,680
but

828
00:44:21,640 --> 00:44:23,350
how can I thank Lord?

829
00:44:25,200 --> 00:44:26,010
Miss Jiang.

830
00:44:26,180 --> 00:44:28,760
Do you know what Lord usually likes?

831
00:44:33,300 --> 00:44:35,030
(Lord is willing to help Ayan,)

832
00:44:35,410 --> 00:44:37,510
so she must thank him.

833
00:44:38,470 --> 00:44:40,550
But he's rich

834
00:44:40,550 --> 00:44:41,970
and has nothing to worry about.

835
00:44:42,640 --> 00:44:44,120
What should she get him?

836
00:45:12,510 --> 00:45:13,970
Are you seeing which one is expensive

837
00:45:13,992 --> 00:45:15,208
and could fetch a good price?

838
00:45:15,208 --> 00:45:15,990
You're just in time.

839
00:45:16,200 --> 00:45:17,280
What gift would you like?

840
00:45:17,990 --> 00:45:18,470
Me?

841
00:45:18,760 --> 00:45:19,300
Yes.

842
00:45:19,530 --> 00:45:21,510
What kind of gifts
do men like to receive?

843
00:45:23,200 --> 00:45:24,050
I don't know.

844
00:45:24,640 --> 00:45:26,180
How could you not know?

845
00:45:27,350 --> 00:45:28,240
I never received one.

846
00:45:28,910 --> 00:45:30,390
Has no one ever given you a gift?

847
00:45:31,010 --> 00:45:32,430
They need to have the nerve to do so.

848
00:45:34,800 --> 00:45:36,720
Didn't I give you a sugar people?

849
00:45:38,050 --> 00:45:39,280
Didn't you eat it?

850
00:45:40,530 --> 00:45:42,430
I'll give you one next time then.

851
00:45:43,016 --> 00:45:44,470
It doesn't matter what you give me.

852
00:45:44,872 --> 00:45:46,140
It's the thought that counts.

853
00:46:11,273 --> 00:46:16,133
♪Pluck a red bean, cherish you♪

854
00:46:16,753 --> 00:46:19,273
♪Deep within♪

855
00:46:20,323 --> 00:46:25,123
♪A flower of affection blooms
